Package org.middleheaven.global.atlas Description

Atlas Toolbox Provides culture agnostic representations for Country, CountryDivision and Town. This package relies on ISO standards for code-naming countries, cities and country divisions thus providing out-of-the box high level atlas information. Each country developers can extends this model on their own application.
